GlideApp (Garmin ConnectIQ) App
===============================
Privacy information

GlideApp does not collect and transmit any data to any 3rd-party, save for the
Activity files you record and upload to Garmin (Connect) when synchronizing
your device.

The permissions required by GliderSK are:
 - "Sensor" permission:
   for barometric pressure (elevation)
 - "Positioning" permission:
   for location and speed data
 - "Fit" permission:
   for recording your Activity (to FIT file)
 - "FitContributor" permission:
   to add oxygen saturation, barometric altitude and vertical speed in your
   recorded Activity (FIT file)
